also have a power coating system for around $60:00. in a book i love called 
HOW TO RESTORE YOUR COLLECTOR CAR. BY  TOM BROWNELL any library can get it for 
you, he tells how to remove paint grease ect by using a wash tub metal barrel 
or any thing large enough to hold your wheels fenders ect by building a fire 
to heat the water then adding lye to remove all paint hope this is a help to 
